nd downstream loans, questions of capital maintenance and a potential liability for losses alerts the reader to crucial requirements, provisions and points, which are most important to deal with in the chosen configuration for the cash pool system Readership: Business and bank lawyers, in-house law departments of companies, banks' legal departments.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCash management. 7aLAW / Securities.2bisacsh1 aBade, Måriella, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBattaglia, Giuseppe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBohan, Daragh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBurke, Louis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDaly, Avril, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrątczak, Klaudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGambini, Luca, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGarcia, Nuno de Oliveira, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoldenberg, Russell, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGörgényi, Orsolya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIlum, Mads, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJansen, Justus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJansen, Justus, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aJędrezejak, Jakub, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKalińska, Magdalena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKallas, Kadri, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKloppers, Jaap, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov